#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:1
msgid "QuickStart"
msgstr "快速开始"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:7
msgid "Basic Usage Snippets"
msgstr "基本用法示例"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:9
msgid "How to Use Flex-Flash-Attention"
msgstr "如何使用 Flex-Flash-Attention"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:12
msgid ""
"The following snippet shows how to call `flex_flash_attn_func` for the non-"
"distributed (i.e., single-GPU) scenario with a minimal workflow: "
"configuration, tensor initialization, and calculate attention for both "
"forward and backward passes."
msgstr ""
"以下代码片段展示了如何在非分布式（即单 GPU）场景中调用 "
"`flex_flash_attn_func`，包含最小工作流程：配置、张量初始化，以及前向和反向传播的注意力计算。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:80
msgid "How to Use MagiAttention"
msgstr "如何使用 MagiAttention"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:83
msgid ""
"The snippet below illustrates a full distributed workflow: environment setup"
" (*via torchrun*), dist-attn runtime key creation, dispatch/undispatch, "
"distributed attention calculation for both forward and backward passes, as "
"well as an example of handling gradient reduction of attention sink."
msgstr ""
"以下代码片段展示了完整的分布式工作流程：环境设置（*通过 torchrun*）、dist-attn "
"运行时密钥创建、dispatch/undispatch、前向和反向传播的分布式注意力计算，以及处理 attention sink 梯度归约的示例。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:265
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "示例"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:268
msgid ""
"The following examples are a work in progress. More complete and detailed "
"examples will be provided in a future update."
msgstr "以下示例仍在完善中。更完整、更详细的示例将在后续更新中提供。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:271
msgid "Integration with FSDP2"
msgstr "与 FSDP2 集成"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:273
msgid ""
"An example demonstrating how to integrate MagiAttention with FSDP2 is "
"provided in [examples/torch_native](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/tree/main/examples/torch_native). Use the included "
"`run.sh` to execute the example."
msgstr ""
"在 [examples/torch_native](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/tree/main/examples/torch_native) 中提供了一个展示如何将 MagiAttention"
" 与 FSDP2 集成的示例。使用其中包含的 `run.sh` 来运行该示例。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:275
msgid ""
"This example constructs a LLaMA-1B model and demonstrates applying FSDP2 "
"with MagiAttention as the parallelism strategy."
msgstr "此示例构建了一个 LLaMA-1B 模型，并演示了将 FSDP2 与 MagiAttention 作为并行策略的应用。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:277
msgid ""
"`examples/torch_native/modeling_llama.py`: Model construction and "
"MagiAttention integration."
msgstr "`examples/torch_native/modeling_llama.py`：模型构建与 MagiAttention 集成。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:278
msgid "`examples/torch_native/main.py`: Training loop and execution script."
msgstr "`examples/torch_native/main.py`：训练循环与执行脚本。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:281
msgid "Integration with Megatron-LM"
msgstr "与 Megatron-LM 集成"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:283
msgid ""
"We maintain a repository [Megatron-LM-"
"MagiAttention](https://github.com/SandAI-org/Megatron-LM-"
"MagiAttention/tree/magi_attention) that demonstrates integrating "
"MagiAttention with Megatron-LM. The repository is forked from [Megatron-LM "
"v0.11.0](https://github.com/NVIDIA/Megatron-LM/tree/v0.11.0) and provides a "
"working example for training LLaMA-1B with Megatron-LM + MagiAttention. We "
"also include experiment logs for a LLaMA-3-1B training run to validate "
"convergence."
msgstr ""
"我们维护了一个仓库 [Megatron-LM-MagiAttention](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/Megatron-LM-MagiAttention/tree/magi_attention)，展示了如何将 MagiAttention 与 "
"Megatron-LM 集成。该仓库 fork 自 [Megatron-LM "
"v0.11.0](https://github.com/NVIDIA/Megatron-LM/tree/v0.11.0)，提供了使用 Megatron-"
"LM + MagiAttention 训练 LLaMA-1B 的可运行示例。我们还包含了 LLaMA-3-1B 训练运行的实验日志以验证收敛性。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:285
msgid ""
"For more information, consult [examples/megatron](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/tree/main/examples/megatron)."
msgstr ""
"更多信息请参阅 [examples/megatron](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/tree/main/examples/megatron)。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:288
msgid "Integration with Transformers"
msgstr "与 Transformers 集成"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:290
msgid ""
"An integration example for transformers is available in "
"[examples/transformers](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/tree/main/examples/transformers)."
msgstr ""
"Transformers 的集成示例可在 [examples/transformers](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/tree/main/examples/transformers) 中获取。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/quickstart.md:292
msgid ""
"We used this integration to run a continued-training experiment on "
"LLaMA-3-1B and validated MagiAttention convergence."
msgstr "我们使用此集成在 LLaMA-3-1B 上进行了继续训练实验，并验证了 MagiAttention 的收敛性。"
